Here you will find the highest rated articles on the site written in a Group of Interest format. Voting is restricted to site members, to avoid vandalism.

GoI Formats are stories written within the Foundation universe from the perspective of an organization that is not the SCP Foundation. [[[groups of interest|Click here to see all Groups of Interest,]]] and [[[goi-formats| click here to see all GoI Formats]]].

